data.meta_description: Giysi - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists contact information for 35 companies involved in clothes production in Uzbekistan. It provides the company name, contact phone numbers and email, legal name, brand name, and physical address for each business. The companies are located across various regions of Uzbekistan, primarily in Tashkent, and work in fields like textiles, sewing, fashion, and clothing retail.
